D:\mathbb{R}[X] \to \mathbb{R}[X]
D(f(X))=f'(X) .
e^{tD}(f(X)) = f(X+t)
t \in \mathbb{R}
X^n
P(X)
P(X+t)=\sum_{k=0}^n \frac{P^{(k)}(X)}{k!} t^k=\left(\sum_{k=0}^n \frac{D^k}{k!} t^k\right) P(X)
P(X+t)
e^{tD}=\sum_{k=0}^\infty \frac{D^k}{k!} t^k
D^{n+1}P=0
P
P(X+t)=e^{tD}P(X)
e^{tD}
p(X)=\sum_{k=0}^m a_kX^k
e^{tD}p(X) = \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{1}{n!}t^nD^n\left(\sum_{k=0}^m a_kX^k\right) = \sum_{n=0}^m \frac{1}{n!}t^nD^n\left(\sum_{k=0}^m a_kX^k\right) = \sum_{k=0}^m a_k\left(\sum_{n=0}^m \frac{1}{n!}t^nD^nX^k\right) = \sum_{k=0}^m a_k\left(\sum_{n=0}^k \frac{1}{n!}t^nD^nX^k\right)
